    "System.out.println(domReadCorrect ? \"Part 4a (DOM read): passed!\" : \"Part 4a (DOM read): not quite \\u2014 check your TODO and re-run.\");"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f5b133b1",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**4b.** Now do something SAX and StAX *cannot* do: modify the parsed\n",
    "tree. Build a new `<address>` element (with `forename`, `surname`, `email`,\n",
    "and `powerlevel` children) and append it to the root. Fill in the two\n",
    "`// TODO` lines."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "32ce9458",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import org.w3c.dom.Element;\n",
    "\n",
    "Element newAddress = addressBookDoc.createElement(\"address\");\n",
    "\n",
    "Element newForename = addressBookDoc.createElement(\"forename\");\n",
    "newForename.setTextContent(\"Lingyang\");\n",
    "\n",
    "Element newSurname = addressBookDoc.createElement(\"surname\");\n",
    "newSurname.setTextContent(\"\");\n",
    "\n",
    "Element newEmail = addressBookDoc.createElement(\"email\");\n",
    "newEmail.setTextContent(\"thunder@rinascita.com\");\n",
    "\n",
    "Element newPowerlevel = addressBookDoc.createElement(\"powerlevel\");\n",
    "newPowerlevel.setTextContent(\"-500\");\n",
    "\n",
    "// TODO: append newForename, newSurname, newEmail, and newPowerlevel as children of newAddress (four calls to appendChild)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "Element addressBookRoot = addressBookDoc.getDocumentElement();\n",
    "// TODO: append newAddress as a child of addressBookRoot\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "NodeList updatedAddresses = addressBookDoc.getElementsByTagName(\"address\");\n",
    "System.out.println(\"Addresses after edit: \" + updatedAddresses.getLength());"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "7cb5a02a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Checker for 4b:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "35ee212b",
   "metadata": {},
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
