   "source": [
    "## All done\n",
    "\n",
    "That covers all three technologies. If you want a one-line summary to\n",
    "keep in mind:\n",
    "\n",
    "- **SAX** \u2014 push, fast, read-only, one node at a time.\n",
    "- **StAX** \u2014 pull, also fast and serial, but can additionally write XML.\n",
    "- **DOM** \u2014 full tree in memory, slowest/heaviest, but the only one that\n",
    "  lets you navigate freely and modify the document."
   ]
